    <item>
      <title>据报道，拜登正考虑退出，面临越来越大的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，《纽约时报》刊登了一则爆炸性报道称，拜登向一位关键盟友承认，如果他在未来几天无法扭转公众舆论，他可能不得不放弃竞选连任，这进一步加剧了要求总统乔·拜登退出总统竞选的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞的父亲不适合陪同她参加欧盟资金丑闻审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-s-father-unfit-to-join-her-in-trial-over-eu-funds-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞年迈的父亲让-玛丽因涉嫌挪用数百万欧元欧盟资金在法国搭建平台而被认为不适合与她一起接受审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-s-father-unfit-to-join-her-in-trial-over-eu-funds-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:10:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非税务部长欢迎财政部任命</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/south-africa-s-tax-boss-welcomes-finance-ministry-appointments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非税务主管爱德华·基斯韦特 (Edward Kieswetter) 对财政部长伊诺克·戈东瓦纳 (Enoch Godongwana) 及其副手戴维·马松多 (David Masondo) 的连任表示欢迎，并表示在他们的领导下，该国将继续走可持续的财政整顿道路，以促进经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/south-africa-s-tax-boss-welcomes-finance-ministry-appointments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:52:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京自五月以来第二次会见习近平，两国领导人高度评价两国关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/putin-meets-xi-for-second-time-since-may-as-leaders-hail-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在不到两个月内第二次会见中国国家主席习近平，大力宣扬俄罗斯与中国的“全面伙伴关系”，凸显莫斯科与北京的深度融合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/putin-meets-xi-for-second-time-since-may-as-leaders-hail-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大选前一天，默多克旗下《太阳报》支持斯塔默领导的工党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/murdoch-s-sun-endorses-starmer-s-labour-the-day-before-uk-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲁珀特·默多克的《太阳报》支持基尔·斯塔默及其反对党工党赢得英国大选，这是英国媒体界的戏剧性举动，反映出该国政局的瞬息万变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/murdoch-s-sun-endorses-starmer-s-labour-the-day-before-uk-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:28:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚内阁组建尝试失败 提前投票迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/bulgaria-edges-closer-to-snap-vote-as-cabinet-attempt-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由前总理博伊科·鲍里索夫领导的 Gerb 党支持的保加利亚少数派政府周三未能获得议会支持，导致该国政治危机延续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/bulgaria-edges-closer-to-snap-vote-as-cabinet-attempt-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:04:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞的竞争对手在阻止极右翼执政的努力中遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-s-far-right-faces-a-struggle-as-rivals-band-together</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派阵营和左翼联盟策略性地从法国立法选举第二轮中撤出数百名候选人，以降低玛丽娜·勒庞的极右翼国民联盟获得绝对多数的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-s-far-right-faces-a-struggle-as-rivals-band-together</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
